# 2026-06-30 — Phase 3 Slice 5 CP2: Discount Rules API + Web UI

## Starting state

CP1 closed on 2026-06-29 (commit `b228098`). It delivered:
- `DiscountRule` Prisma model + enums (`DiscountDuration`, `DiscountType`)
- Migration with FORCE RLS + tenant-isolation policy + RBAC seed
- `createDiscountRuleSchema` / `updateDiscountRuleSchema` in `packages/types` with 5 Zod `.refine()` guards
- `DiscountRuleService` with full CRUD + audit log on every mutation
- 20 integration tests (all green)

Product decisions locked in CP1:
- Manual only — no rule engine, no auto-triggering
- `PERCENTAGE` capped at 9999 basis points (99.99%); 100% must use `FULL_WAIVER`
- `value: Int?` — NULL for `FULL_WAIVER`, positive int for others
- Scope: exactly one of `feeItemId` XOR `feeCategoryId`
- Permissions: `discount-rule.read/create/update/deactivate` (no hard delete)

