## Notable decisions

**`includeInactive: true` on discount modal pickers** — discount rules outlive the
active lifespan of fee categories and items. A bursar needs to see all targets
regardless of active state when assigning or reviewing discounts.

**`cache: "no-store"` is global in `apiFetch`** — none of the NestJS endpoints should
be served from the HTTP cache (freshness is managed by React Query / component state,
not HTTP headers). This is correct for an authenticated API client.

**Academic years empty = data not yet created** — if the year/term duration picker
shows no years, the school must add academic years via Settings → Academic Years first.
No code change required; the console.error will surface API-level errors if they occur.

